Justin Prime - Insane is OUT NOW!
https://skink.lnk.to/JustinPrimeInsane

Kicking things off with a pulsating drumbeat and a progressive build featuring winding synths and euphoric melodies, ‘Insane’ emanates main stage madness from start to finish. Destined to be one of the summer’s biggest festival anthems, ‘Insane’ follows a string of high-end cuts crafted up by Justin Prime in the past few years.
